Why this file is committed to the repo
--------------------------------------
qmd-gd vendors this model so a fresh clone can embed with no network access —
required for environments where huggingface.co is unreachable (e.g. behind a
corporate proxy). It is the default embedding model, referenced internally by
the stable identity "bundled:bge-small-en-v1.5-Q8_0.gguf".

Override with QMD_EMBED_MODEL=<absolute path to a .gguf> or an hf:<user>/<repo>/<file>
URI to use a different model.

